import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Nav, NavItem, NavLink } from 'reactstrap'

class Footer extends Component{
  render(){
    return(
      <React.Fragment>
        <Nav>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to="/">Home</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to="/catindex">All the Cats</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
          <NavItem>
            <NavLink to="catnew">And a New Cat</NavLink>
          </NavItem>
        </Nav>
      </React.Fragment>
    )
  }
}
export default Footer
